<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v15" title="Q1_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un informe de cálculo se describe: «Para obtener cierto resultado, se utiliza la operación 5 − (−4)·(−3 − 5). La profesora resalta que primero se debe evaluar el paréntesis, luego la multiplicación y finalmente la resta con 5». ¿Cuál es el valor de la operación 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mo>−</m:mo>
              <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mo>−</m:mo>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              <m:mo>−</m:mo>
              <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      ?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">37<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al evaluar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el valor no es 37.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">−27<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Primero, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Después, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Finalmente, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, la respuesta correcta es −27.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">13<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al evaluar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el valor no es 13.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">27<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al evaluar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el valor no es 27.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Resolver el paréntesis interior</strong></p>
            <p>La operación es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                      <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Primero se calcula:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces la expresión queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Resolver la multiplicación</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora se calcula:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esto ocurre porque el producto de dos números negativos es positivo.</p>
            <p>La expresión queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Resolver la resta final</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>27</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de la operación es <strong>−27</strong>, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>